data.description: Check out this adorable 3 bedroom 1 1/2 bath home. Many updates have been done for you. Most windows, fresh paint, new sliding glass door leading to the new patio are perfect for those summer family gatherings. This home also offers a full basement, partially finished for extra living space. A great home for a growing family.
